{"tid":567924,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"5** 心得之少少分享","createTime":"2018-02-21T09:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T06:21:15.000Z","uid":7542,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3834d510d1e82ccd9fe967c67820bb8d395f00b1","tid":567924,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:44:36.000Z","msg":"[size=1]如果大家可以集中一齊分享 5** 嘅心得咁就好啦[/size=3] <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好耐好耐之前喺舊登開過 post 分享<strong>中文同通識 5**</strong> 既心得，點知比個垃圾 admin del 咗  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家就快要考 DSE，所以我都想分享少少，睇吓可唔可以幫到大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一齊戰勝中文同通識兩個唔知想點嘅考試！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS 大家如果對<strong>英文</strong>有興趣我都可以分享吓~ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">// 中文</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n自問無能力幫人補中文改作文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過都希望分享一下溫習心得及應試技巧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但有個問題就係中文依家考試制度轉咗，<br />\n<br />\n所以我都唔係好識玩，但考語文科背後套技巧應該都可以應用到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一種題目你一定要啱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qn8D-3F5Tik\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQn8D-3F5Tik&d=QTcD7cvUk5BaeGQS6jHlGpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=62436918\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Qn8D-3F5Tik</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n考得差因為無運？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KvFB-xOGvis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKvFB-xOGvis&d=QTcD7cvUk5BaeGQS6jHlGpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=96753aa6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KvFB-xOGvis</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應試心理學<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AD2Tuj3p4bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAD2Tuj3p4bo&d=QTcD7cvUk5BaeGQS6jHlGpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b6d6d323\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AD2Tuj3p4bo</a>"},{"pid":"bf598c247eeb62f0a089219e87b9c64033a3ce78","tid":567924,"uid":142872,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:51:11.000Z","msg":"我右分享下先<br />\n我中英數通electives全裸考<br />\n自問有能力5**<br />\n最後出黎全部1左<br />\n肯定係個考官太on9"},{"pid":"d94a4b6291cbb9f5506c4da569a00096fd262963","tid":567924,"uid":152589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:53:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"d089d137c1526ef3945370f0622f157b086bcb7b","tid":567924,"uid":129039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"074cfb864d76921d03201b643023df549fbdb2b1","tid":567924,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T10:01:41.000Z","msg":"中文5**<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b77f9a436e68b69e6354d731e2f48ba7589331","tid":567924,"uid":137555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"074cfb864d76921d03201b643023df549fbdb2b1","tid":567924,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T10:01:41.000Z","msg":"中文5**<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T10:13:13.000Z","msg":"恩師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17a6f2a5be55be55934c299727a51d8106ce6e1","tid":567924,"uid":42374,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d1b77f9a436e68b69e6354d731e2f48ba7589331","tid":567924,"uid":137555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"074cfb864d76921d03201b643023df549fbdb2b1","tid":567924,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T10:01:41.000Z","msg":"中文5**<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/